<blockquote>
  <p>Ni Z, Hu H. Let it go: central neural control of urination. <a href="https://www.nature.com/articles/s41593-018-0259-1.pdf"><strong>Nature Neuroscience</strong></a>. [<a href="http://www.hailanhu-lab.net/uploads/2018/10/301931072751.pdf">pdf]</a></p>
